      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Add reset family carryover summaries",
        "body": "## Behavior or issue addressed\n\nDepends on #90239.\n\nWhen a session has been reset/rotated, the active transcript can be clean while the previous reset archive still contains the latest compaction summary. The next embedded-agent prompt therefore starts without the carryover context unless the model/tool explicitly asks for family history.\n\nThis change reuses the session-family transcript resolver from #90239 and injects the latest reset-archive compaction summary into embedded-agent prompt context before the LLM boundary, but only when the active context does not already contain a compaction summary.\n\n## Fix\n\n- Move the #90239 family/reset transcript target resolver into a shared gateway helper.\n- Keep `chat.history(includeFamily)` on the shared resolver.\n- Pass the current session store path/entry into embedded-agent attempts.\n- Add a prompt-context transform that prepends one `compactionSummary` from reset ancestor transcripts.\n- Skip injection when the active session already has a compaction summary.\n- Cap family transcript read targets before reading files; ancestor targets stop at the cap while current-session targets remain available.\n- Rebased onto current `origin/main` and preserved the newer transcript-reader seam plus same-session reset fallback.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n**Current head proven:** `90525a0927bfcd94912dfa9c3d702c6de6cb231d`.\n\n**Behavior or issue addressed:** A reset/rotated logical session should read bounded reset-family history through the shared resolver, keep current reset archive plus current active transcript available inside the cap, inject exactly one reset-family compaction summary before the embedded-agent LLM boundary, and cap oversized archived summaries before prompt injection.\n\n**Real environment tested:** Local OpenClaw checkout on this PR branch at `/home/clever/.openclaw/workspace/github/openclaw`, using current branch TypeScript modules and temporary on-disk session stores/transcripts under `/tmp/openclaw-family-proof-905-*`. No private channel, endpoint, phone, prompt, or auth data was used.\n\n**Exact steps or command run after this patch:**\n\n```text\n$ git rev-parse HEAD\n90525a0927bfcd94912dfa9c3d702c6de6cb231d\n\n$ node --import tsx --input-type=module <<'TS'\n# The script imported these current-branch modules:\n# - ./src/gateway/session-history-family.ts\n# - ./src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/session-family-carryover.ts\n# It created a temporary sessions.json, 35 ancestor transcripts,\n# one current reset archive transcript, and one current active transcript.\n# Ancestor 29 contained an oversized compaction summary larger than\n# CARRYOVER_SUMMARY_MAX_CHARS. The script called the real family target\n# resolver, real carryover resolver, installed the prompt transform,\n# applied the transform twice, printed the observed result, and removed temp files.\nTS\n{\n  \"head\": \"90525a0927bfcd94912dfa9c3d702c6de6cb231d\",\n  \"targetCount\": 32,\n  \"firstTargets\": [\n    \"ancestor-proof-00:ancestor\",\n    \"ancestor-proof-01:ancestor\",\n    \"ancestor-proof-02:ancestor\"\n  ],\n  \"lastTargets\": [\n    \"ancestor-proof-29:ancestor\",\n    \"current-proof-session:reset-archive\",\n    \"current-proof-session:active\"\n  ],\n  \"currentResetTargetPresent\": true,\n  \"currentActiveLast\": true,\n  \"ancestor29Present\": true,\n  \"ancestor30Present\": false,\n  \"ancestor34Present\": false,\n  \"carryoverSummaryLength\": 16384,\n  \"carryoverSummaryMaxChars\": 16384,\n  \"carryoverSummaryEndsTruncated\": true,\n  \"carryoverSummaryPrefix\": \"Exact-head 905 oversized carryover 29: x\",\n  \"carryoverTokensBefore\": 2029,\n  \"promptRolesBeforeLlm\": [\n    \"compactionSummary\",\n    \"user\"\n  ],\n  \"compactionSummaryCount\": 1,\n  \"idempotentRoles\": [\n    \"compactionSummary\",\n    \"user\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Evidence after fix:**\n\n- The shared resolver returned 32 targets and kept both current reset archive and current active transcript inside the cap.\n- The current active transcript was ordered last for final history trimming.\n- Ancestors beyond the reserved cap were not read: `ancestor30Present` and `ancestor34Present` are false.\n- Carryover selected the latest ancestor inside the capped family window, `ancestor-proof-29`, and preserved its token count.\n- The oversized archived compaction summary was capped before prompt injection: `carryoverSummaryLength` equals `carryoverSummaryMaxChars` (16384) and `carryoverSummaryEndsTruncated` is true.\n- The embedded prompt transform injected exactly one `compactionSummary` before the model boundary and remained idempotent on a second pass.\n\n**Observed result after fix:** The terminal output showed `targetCount: 32`, current reset archive plus current active transcript retained at the end of the target list, `ancestor30Present: false`, `ancestor34Present: false`, one pre-LLM `compactionSummary`, idempotent second transform roles, and an oversized summary capped exactly at 16384 chars with `[summary truncated]`.\n\n**Validation on current head:**\n\n```text\n$ CI=true node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/gateway/server.sessions.reset-models.test.ts\nTest Files  2 passed (2)\nTests  20 passed (20)\n\n$ CI=true node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/session-family-carryover.test.ts\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  8 passed (8)\n\n$ git diff --check\n# no output\n\n$ CI=true node --import tsx scripts/generate-prompt-snapshots.ts --check\nPrompt snapshots are current (7 files).\n\n$ CI=true node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.test.src.json\n# passed\n```\n\n**What was not tested:** Full live Telegram/Slack/Discord end-to-end reset turn was not run locally; the proof exercises the real resolver and embedded carryover path against on-disk OpenClaw-like session artifacts.\n\n\n\n\n",
